      <title>尽管利润未达预期，英国石油公司仍维持股票回购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/bp-maintains-share-buybacks-even-as-profit-misses-estimates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管天然气价格下跌导致第一季度利润降幅超过预期，英国石油公司仍维持股票回购的步伐。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/bp-maintains-share-buybacks-even-as-profit-misses-estimates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:12:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银的埃尔莫蒂：我们看到“我们的业务有资金流入”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-07/ubs-s-ermotti-we-see-inflows-across-our-businesses-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂 (Sergio Ermotti) 讨论了该银行在经历两个亏损季度后恢复盈利后的业绩和前景。埃尔莫蒂在苏黎世接受彭博社记者弗朗辛·拉夸 (Francine Lacqua) 采访时表示，该银行“客户发展势头良好，各业务部门资金流入，资本充足”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-07/ubs-s-ermotti-we-see-inflows-across-our-businesses-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 06:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
