      <title>摩根大通在亚洲裁员至少七个投资银行职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/jpmorgan-starts-new-round-of-investment-banking-job-cuts-in-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，摩根大通公司已在亚洲启动新一轮裁员计划，将削减至少 7 个投资银行职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/jpmorgan-starts-new-round-of-investment-banking-job-cuts-in-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:56:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>沙特阿拉伯国家石油公司在沙特预算赤字中保持 310 亿美元的支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/aramco-to-pay-31-billion-dividend-as-saudi-posts-budget-deficit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管利润较低，但阿美公司仍向沙特政府和其他投资者派发 310 亿美元的股息，这对正在与预算赤字作斗争的沙特经济来说是一个福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/aramco-to-pay-31-billion-dividend-as-saudi-posts-budget-deficit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:38:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
